<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Greenfield University</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Merriweather:wght@400;700&family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            color: #333;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #004d00;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2em 1em;
        }
        header h1 {
            font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;
            font-size: 3em;
            margin: 0;
        }
        nav {
            background-color: #006400;
            padding: 1em;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 0.75em 1.5em;
            margin: 0 0.5em;
            background-color: #004d00;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            background-color: #003300;
        }
        main {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 2em auto;
            padding: 2em;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .hero {
            background-image: url('/images/campus.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 6em 1em;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 2em;
            position: relative;
        }
        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;
            font-size: 4em;
            margin: 0;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        section {
            margin-bottom: 3em;
        }
        section h2 {
            font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;
            color: #004d00;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 0.5em;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #004d00;
            display: inline-block;
            padding-bottom: 0.2em;
        }
        section p, section ul {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        ul li {
            margin-bottom: 0.75em;
            padding-left: 1.5em;
            position: relative;
        }
        ul li::before {
            content: 'â€¢';
            color: #004d00;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: -0.2em;
        }
        img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-top: 1em;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #004d00;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2em 1em;
            margin-top: 3em;
        }
        footer p {
            margin: 0.5em 0;
        }
        footer a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 0.5em;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Greenfield University</h1>
        <p>Empowering the next generation of leaders in environmental studies and sustainable technologies.</p>
    </header>
    <nav>
        <a href="/register">Apply</a>
        <a href="/courses">Programs/Degrees</a>
        <a href="/about">About Us</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact Us</a>
        <a href="/login">Login</a>
        <a href="/faculty/register">Register as Faculty</a>
        <a href="/admin/register">Register as Admin</a>
    </nav>
    <main>
        <div class="hero">
            <h1>Welcome to Greenfield University</h1>
            <p>Join us in shaping a sustainable future.</p>
        </div>
        <section id="apply">
            <h2>Apply Now</h2>
            <p>Join our vibrant community of learners at Greenfield University. Applications for the Fall 2025 semester are now open!</p>
            <img src="/images/BOYYYYY.jpeg" alt="Students applying to Greenfield University">
        </section>
        <section id="programs">
            <h2>Programs and Degrees</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Bachelor of Science in Environmental Studies</li>
                <li>Master of Arts in Sustainable Development</li>
                <li>Ph.D. in Renewable Energy Technologies</li>
            </ul>
            <img src="/images/degree.jpeg" alt="Greenfield University campus">
        </section>
        <section id="about">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>Greenfield University, established in 2010, is a leading institution in environmental studies and sustainable technologies. Our campus, nestled in the heart of the Green Valley, provides a perfect backdrop for our innovative programs.</p>
            <img src="/images/College people.jpeg" alt="Greenfield University campus">
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 Greenfield University. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>
            <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> |
            <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a> |
            <a href="/contact">Contact Us</a>
        </p>
    </footer>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>